Definition: the quality of being a conclusion or opinion based on supposition and conjecture rather than on fact or investigation
Example: her work is highly contentious because of its speculativeness and lack of supporting evidence
Synonyms: adj, all, theoretical, speculative, uncertainty, the, quality, of, being, a, conclusion, or, opinion, based, on, supposition, and, conjecture, rather, than, fact, investigation, her, work, is, highly, contentious, because, its, lack, supporting, evidence
Category: noun.attribute
